### Manual Installation

**Standard config** works in most tools:

```js
{
  "servers": {
    "Hoge-Name": {
      "command": "uv",
      "args": [
        "run",
        "--directory",
        "{{ package_path }}",
        "-m",
        "{{ package_name }}"
      ],
      "env": {}
    }
  }
}
```

